# EcoFill System â€“ Automated Water Conservation Robot

## Description
**EcoFill System** monitors water usage and automates water filling to reduce waste. It ensures efficient water management for households and gardens.

## Technologies Used
- Arduino UNO  
- Water Level Sensors  
- Relay Modules  
- Python  

## Key Features
- Automated water filling  
- Waste reduction  
- Easy integration with tanks and taps  

## My Role
Designed automation logic, installed sensors, and tested water level management.

